      • setMapVenue

        public boolean setMapVenue(MappedInVenue venue)
        Call this method to set this map activity's main venue. This will start all the background tasks to start downloading all map and location data for this venue. Make sure the device is connected to the Internet, otherwise this method will fail.
        Parameters:
        venue - The MappedIn venue to display in the map
        Returns:
        true if venue loading started. false if an error occurred.

      • shouldExitMap

        public boolean shouldExitMap()
        This method is called right before onBackPressed() is about to close or exit the activity. It is called mainly to check if it is okay to close this activity or not.

        If you want the map activity to close then just return true. However, if you do not want to close the activity yet as you still have some pending tasks left to do then you should return false.
        Returns:
        true to close or exit the activity. false to do nothing.
